                <h3><em>Good Will Hunting</em></h3>

                <div class="poster-wrap">
                    <img src="images/goodwillhunting-poster.jpg" alt="Good Will Hunting movie poster">
                </div>

                <p>
                    <em>Good Will Hunting</em> is a 1997 drama directed by Gus Van Sant. The film follows Will Hunting, a young janitor at MIT who is secretly a mathematical genius. When his talent is discovered, he is pushed to work with a therapist and a professor, forcing him to confront his troubled past and decide what he really wants out of life. The movie is both a story about raw intellect and about the emotional walls people build to protect themselves from being hurt.
                </p>

