                <h3><em>Dead Poets Society</em></h3>

                <div class="poster-wrap">
                    <img src="images/deadpoetssociety-poster.jpg" alt="Dead Poets Society movie poster">
                </div>

                <p>
                    <em>Dead Poets Society</em> is a 1989 drama directed by Peter Weir. Set at the fictional Welton Academy, a strict all-boys preparatory school in Vermont, the film follows a group of students whose lives are changed by their new English teacher, John Keating. Keating encourages his students to think for themselves, embrace poetry, and seize the day. The film is a moving exploration of conformity, passion, and the cost of following your own voice in a world that demands silence.
                </p>

